nodes.text: Docking Bay 66 was a docking bay located in the Mezenti Spaceport on Nar Shaddaa during the Cold War.

Docking Bay 66 appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic during the Imperial Agent class mission on Nar Shaddaa. The player only visits the docking bay after making the Light Side choice, deciding to pursuit Watcher X, instead of letting him go.
